{"tid":2294604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有報道指美國國防部擬擴大中國企業黑名單至35間","createTime":"2020-11-21T06:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T11:05:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93761f613512362795b9c00483f8e3d04b76d9c6","tid":2294604,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:53:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561154-20201121.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561154-20201121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM33hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=09e4f51c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561154-20201121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=355dbc74\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561154-20201121.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社引述消息人士報道，美國政府將在國防部的制裁名單中，再加多4間中國企業，令受影響的中國企業增加至35間，將會限制美國投資者對這些企業進行投資。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在上星期簽署行政命令，制裁31間中國企業，指控這些企業受中國軍方擁有或控制，這些企業包括海康威視、中國電信及中國移動等。<br />\n<br />\n報道表示，國防部最快在當地星期五公布這些企業的名單，亦可能到下星期公布。<br />\n<br />\n白宮暫時未有回應。"},{"pid":"6910e24e87230ba8d626044d5162417814e67734","tid":2294604,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:57:14.000Z","msg":"口交部：美國繼續犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c25cf3effd4b0732d34edb5cb09634819188e8d","tid":2294604,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"d828fba7c9a01a275720864cf58f9eb26f565964","tid":2294604,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:19:47.000Z","msg":"y not all？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6dbc87a846459fc6efb090f4886984790958c4","tid":2294604,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,